{
  "stem": "1680.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 457.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he wanted to put the little seal, which was a K, that meant probably concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I says, no, that I'm not a businessman anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he changed the seal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he put a big seal on this, which I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I pushed in my Judenpass, which I didn't need it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, for some reason I did this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it came out handy very-- handy later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he put this big seal on this paper too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came home, the next day, during the night, the Judenrat was ordered all the Jewish ordnungsdienst, you know, the Jewish police people, to come to go around with the list to tell people to come out to the deportation.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of people didn't want to come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the SS were very wild for this, and they start grabbing people, regardless, whatever the seal was, regardless.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't honor anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they grabbed people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they shot at the same day 10,000 people in the city and about 8,000 people they deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the 11th of June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was called the first deportation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was taking place three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Thursday the 11th, Monday the 15th, and the next Thursday the 18th-- all three days was called first deportation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the second day, I knew Margot at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were friendly, but we weren't tied in any way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went up to their house before, during the registration, and I told them to go and hide-- her and her parents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So her father didn't want hear from it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was an older man, and he didn't want to go to hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they told Margot she should go.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
